  <p>Welcome to the official portfolio of Yashwant Kumar Singh, also known as yashwant439 on GitHub. Yashwant is a passionate full-stack web developer, frontend developer, and AI builder based in New Delhi, India. This portfolio showcases Yashwant Singh's developer projects, web development skills, and AI integrations.</p>
  <p>Yashwant Singh developer portfolio features projects built with React, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, Python, and AI/ML technologies. Explore yashwant439 projects including AI-powered healthcare systems, travel booking platforms, smart resume builders, and weather intelligence apps.</p>
  <p>Looking for a web developer? Yashwant Singh is open for internships, freelance opportunities, hackathons, and collaborations. Contact yashwant web developer for your next project.</p>
